Subject: [PATCH 23/24] =?UTF-8?q?FIX=20ATTEMPT:=20rocket.weight=5Fsram=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=80=94=20stage=20conv0=20weights=20into=20on-chip=20SRAM=20+?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20repoint=200x1110;=20widen=20audit=20sweep?=
